{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_03_04",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 03 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ～……\n今のはうまくいったのではなくて！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant Pant…\nThat wasn't good enough?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……悪くはないんだけど\n今ならもっと出来るかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It's not bad‚\nbut I think we can do better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9484011196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな前より踊れるようになってきてるし\nもう少し頑張ってみない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's getting better at dancing‚\nso why don't we try a little harder?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "……わ、私も当然そう思っていましたわ！\nさあ、もう一度やりますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…O-of course I thought so too!\nLet's do it again!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1785738319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、そうだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ you're right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2000001271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな、すっごく疲れてるのに……）\n（それでも練習をやめようとしない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone's so tired…）\n（But they still don't want to stop practicing.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……っ！\nここで……揃える！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant…!\nHere… we synchronize!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "やった！　今のはバッチリじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We did it! That was perfect‚ wasn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね～……これ、なら～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right… If we keep this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん！　大丈夫！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu! Are you okay?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、休んだ方がいいよ。だいぶ練習してるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ you should take a break. We've been practicing for a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なんの～……これくらいへっちゃらですわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nothing… I can handle this much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "もう、意地張らないでみんなで休も、ね？\n……あれ、芽衣ちゃん？　どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ don't be stubborn‚ let's all take a break‚ okay?\n…Huh‚ Mei-chan? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1369836554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ううん、なんでもないよ。休もっか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… no‚ it's nothing. Let's take a break!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1666712443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "（みんなフラフラなのに、すっごく充実した顔をしてる）\n（チア部のみんなもそうだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone is wobbly on their feet‚ but they look so satisfied.）\n（It was the same with the cheer club.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5666712443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "本気……本気……むむむむ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Serious… Serious… Hmmmmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7000045776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストの練習の帰り道",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On their way back from Moon Tempest practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4466697853
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4466697853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "今日の練習はとっても充実していましたわね！\n自分の成長ぶりに惚れ惚れしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today's practice was so fulfilling!\nI'm amazed at how much I've improved.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.9333312989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、そうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.5999979656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……芽衣？　あなた、さっきから一体どうしましたの？\n練習中も考え込んでましたわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mei? What's wrong with you?\nYou've been lost in thought since during practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9999979656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……バレちゃってた？　えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… You noticed? Ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.0333348592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、すずちゃん。すずちゃんも、みんなも……\nどうしてあんなに本気になれるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Suzu. How come you and everyone…\ncan be so serious?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.2666625977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの、藪から棒に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with the sudden question?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.199995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "だって、みんなフラフラになってたでしょ？\nどうしてあんなになっても頑張れるのかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone was exhausted.\nHow come they can push themselves so hard‚ even when they're like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.166666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.799995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの簡単ですわよ。どれだけ辛かろうと、その先に\nあるものを掴む喜びは何物にもかえがたいからですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's easy. No matter how difficult it is‚\nthe joy of achieving something at the end is irreplaceable!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.9066134822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.0333292644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "その先にあるもの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing at the end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.0333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと。私がばっちり決めたのですから\nもうちょっと反応を返してもいいのではなくて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey! I just gave a perfect answer‚\ncan't you at least react a little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.566666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.099995931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei013.m4a",
