      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そう、分かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see. I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.7666656493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 349.7999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei027.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……もやもやさせちゃってごめんなさい\n部長の話を聞いてから、本気について一杯考えたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… I'm sorry for causing you trouble.\nI thought a lot about what it means to be \"serious\" after hearing what you said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.5333745319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei028.m4a",
      "text": "今まで芽衣は、全力で楽しむことが本気だと思ってた\nだから、チア部もアイドルも本気で、全力で楽しんでた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Up until now‚ I thought being serious meant having fun with all my heart.\nThat's why I was being serious about both cheerleading and being an idol‚ enjoying them with all my heart.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.0000411986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 373.333332316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei029.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はこれからもみんなで楽しみたい。でも、チア部の\nみんなにとっての本気と芽衣の本気は違うのも分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to continue having fun with everyone. But I also understood that\nwhat being \"serious\" means to the cheer club is different from what it means to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 380.0510641112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 385.5999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei030.m4a",
      "text": "だから、同じ方向を向くためにまずはみんなの本気を\n大事にする。それで、芽衣もみんなと同じ本気で頑張る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ to make sure we're all on the same page‚ I'm going to prioritize everyone's \"seriousness\" first.\nAnd then‚ I'll work hard with the same \"seriousness\" as everyone else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 390.3000411986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 397.2999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei031.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって、みんなの気持ちが一つになったら……\n今度は芽衣の本気で、みんなと全力で楽しみたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once everyone's feelings are aligned…\nI want to have fun with everyone‚ with all my heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 403.1333745319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei032.m4a",
      "text": "部長が良ければ……全国大会までは\n一緒に活動させてほしいんだけど……どうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's okay with you‚ captain… I'd like to continue participating\nuntil the national tournament…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 413.8000411986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 418.9999989826
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私なりに調べたけど、アイドルの練習は相当大変なん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've done some research‚ and it seems that idol training is quite demanding‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 418.9999989826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でしょ？　チア部の練習だってもっとキツくなるわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "isn't it? Cheer club practice is going to get even tougher too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 423.5050605422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 428.3666656493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei033.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫！　あと少しだけ……\n部長と、チア部のみんなと同じ本気で頑張りたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay! Just a little longer…\nI want to work hard with the same \"seriousness\" as you and the cheer club‚ captain!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 432.4667078653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 438.033332316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ふふ、ここまで言ってくれたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fufu‚ since you've said that much‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 439.5482763144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私も頑張らないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to work hard too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 443.2333745319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 451.7667078653
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei034.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、あと、練習のことなんだけど……\n芽衣、もっと楽しくやりたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ and about practice…\nI want to have more fun with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 451.7667078653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei035.m4a",
      "text": "入部した時と比べるとさ、なんだかみんな、楽しく\n生き生きとした感じじゃなくなってる気がするんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compared to when I first joined‚ it seems like everyone has lost\nthat sense of fun and vibrancy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 461.0000411986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 464.9666656493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei036.m4a",
      "text": "本気で頑張るのも大事だけど……それと同じくらい\n本気で楽しむのも大事だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being serious and working hard is important… but I think it's just as important\nto have fun and enjoy ourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 470.8000411986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "確かに……私も最近ピリついていた気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right… I think I've been a bit on edge lately too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 473.9666656493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "見る人を楽しませるには自分達も楽しまないとよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we want to entertain the audience‚ we need to be enjoying ourselves too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 479.7333745319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 484.3208719453
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かった、練習を始める前にみんなに伝えるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I'll let everyone know before we start practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 484.3208719453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "部長",
      "speakerNameEn": "Leader",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "早坂さん……ありがとう。あと少しだけ、よろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Hayasaka-san… I'm counting on you for a little while longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 489.2333745319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 496.8999888101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei037.m4a",
      "text": "それからのチア部は、ストイックなんだけど\nとっても明るくて……凄くいい雰囲気になった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ the cheer club was still tough‚ but…\nit became much brighter… and the atmosphere was great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 500.9666976927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 507.6333038329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_04-mei038.m4a",
      "text": "そして、全国大会で優勝して……\n芽衣はアイドルを――月ストを選んだんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ we won the national tournament…\nand I chose to be an idol――I chose Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 512.3333460489,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}